Make sure to enable passthrough mode for all service. For each service, request start time, end time and transaction timedout duration details are logged in Soap-UI script log. Detailed fault error message can be found in server.log which is similar to the message below: "org.apache.cxf.interceptor.Fault: Could not send Message. Caused by: java.net.SocketTimeoutException: SocketTimeoutException"

Make sure to enable passthrough mode for all services. For each service, request start time, end time and transaction timedout duration details are logged in Soap-UI script log. Detailed fault error message can be found in server.log which is similar to the message as below: "org.apache.cxf.interceptor.Fault: Could not send Message.
